Path selection to ignore overload node during\nCSPF
      
"head": "boolean", Set if the OL-bit is to be applied to tunnel\nheads

      
"tail": "boolean", Set if the OL-bit is to be applied to tunnel\ntails

      
"mid": "boolean" Set if the OL-bit is to be applied to tunnel\nmidpoints

    },
    : {
Path selection Loose ERO Metric Class\nconfiguration
      : [
No description
        {
          
"metric-type": "string", Metric to use for ERO Expansion

          
"class-type": "integer" Path Selection class Type
range: "0..7"
default: "1"

        }
      ]
    },
    
"tiebreaker": "string", CSPF tiebreaker to use in path calculation

    
"loose-domain-match": "boolean" Use only the IGP instance of the incoming\ninterface

  }
}
